\c 60
\s Dhavhidhi anochema kukundwa kwavo navavengi vavo
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weShushanini Edhuti; rwiyo rweMikitami rwaDhavhidhi, kudzidzisa; panguva yaakarwa naAraminaharaimi naAra- mizobha, Joabhu akadzoka akauraya paMupata woMunyu VaEdhomu vane zvuru zvine gumi nezviviri.
\p
\v 1 Mwari, makatirasi a, makatiparadza; makange makatsamwa; haiwa, tidzorei.
\v 2 Makabvundisa nyika; makaitsemura; gadzirai mitswe yayo; nokuti inozununguka.
\v 3 Makaratidza vanhu venyu zvinhu zvinorema; makatimwisa waini inobata.
\v 4 Makapa vanokutyai mureza, kuti uratidzwe nokuda kwechokwadi.
\v 5 Kuti vadikanwi venyu varwirwe, tiponesei noruoko rwenyu rworudyi, mutipindure.
\p
\v 6 Mwari akataura pautsvene hwake, achiti: Ndichafara kwazvo; ndichaganhura Shekemu, ndichayera mupata weSukoti.
\v 7 Giriyadhi ndeyangu Manase ndeyangu; Efuremuwo inhawiro yomusoro wangu; Judha ndiyo tsvimbo yangu youshe.
\v 8 Moabhu ndiwo mudziyo wangu wokushambidzira; pamusoro peEdhomu ndipo pandichakandira shangu yangu; iwe Firisitia, pururudza nokukunda nokuda kwangu.
\p
\v 9 Ndianiko achandiisa muguta rakasimba? Ndianiko achandiperekedza ndiende Edhomu?
\v 10 Hamuna kutirasi a here, Mwari? Hamubudi Mwari, nehondo dzedu.
\v 11 Tibatsirei pamudzivisi wedu; nokuti kubatsira kwavanhu hakuna maturo.
\v 12 Muna Mwari tichaita noumhare, nokuti ndiye achatsikira vadzivisi vedu pasi.
